Methanoic acid is used in rubber, textile, dyeing, leather and electroplating industries.", "fibs": ["CH3CO2H"]}
{"text": "Ethanoic acid is used as solvent and as vinegar in food industry.", "fibs": ["acid"]}
{"text": "Hexanedioic acid is used in the manufacture of nylon-6, 6.", "fibs": ["acid"]}
{"text": "Esters of benzoic acid are used in perfumery.", "fibs": ["benzoic"]}
